title: Wayna Picchu - Kusichaski
description:
Kusichaski is the perfect music for fans of traditional, unaltered South American folk music. Happy, lively Andean music with native instruments, such as the pan-flute, quena, charango, guitar and drum, put everyone in a good mood. This is an absolute "must-have"!
